<Layout title="IR Signal Flipper">
  <h1>IR Signal Capture & Replay System</h1>

  <p>
    Designed and implemented an interrupt-driven IR signal capture and replay
    system using a PIC18 microcontroller. The system measures pulse timing
    using hardware timers and reproduces signals using PWM modules.
  </p>

